## Additional Terms for IBM Watson Assistant Integration

This project integrates with IBM Watson Assistant services. Users of this project 
must comply with IBM's terms of service and usage policies:

1. **IBM Watson Assistant Terms**: https://www.ibm.com/terms/
2. **IBM Cloud Terms**: https://www.ibm.com/cloud/terms
3. **Watson Assistant Usage**: Users are responsible for their own Watson Assistant 
   service costs and compliance with IBM's usage policies.

